{% comment %}
  "Complete the set" bundle nudge for upsell product pages (ice packs, bottle,
  blanket). Points to the future Rove Day Out Kit bundle once it exists as a
  real Shopify product — upsell.md doesn't have a handle for it yet (unlike
  the three individual products), so until one is set this renders as a
  static callout rather than guessing a link that would 404.

  To activate the link: set `rove_bundle_handle` below to the bundle
  product's real Shopify handle once it's created in Shopify.

  Usage:
  {% render 'rove-bundle-nudge' %}
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'rove-upsell-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign rove_bundle_handle = ''
  assign rove_bundle_product = all_products[rove_bundle_handle]
-%}

{%- if rove_bundle_product != blank and rove_bundle_product.id != blank -%}
  <a href="{{ rove_bundle_product.url }}" class="rove-bundle-nudge">
{%- else -%}
  <!-- ROVE: Day Out Kit bundle product not created in Shopify yet — set rove_bundle_handle in snippets/rove-bundle-nudge.liquid to turn this into a link -->
  <div class="rove-bundle-nudge rove-bundle-nudge--static">
{%- endif -%}

  <span class="rove-bundle-nudge__eyebrow">Complete the set</span>
  <span class="rove-bundle-nudge__heading">The Rove Day Out Kit</span>
  <span class="rove-bundle-nudge__text">
    Cooler, ice packs and blanket together for ~£57.99 — a genuine saving on ~£65.97 bought separately.
  </span>

{%- if rove_bundle_product != blank and rove_bundle_product.id != blank -%}
  </a>
{%- else -%}
  </div>
{%- endif -%}
